You wouldn't have had such great power

124
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:37,080
to affect my business

125
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:39,810
and my Family First app, either.

126
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:45,690
Your Family First?

127
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,970
I remember the year that my dad passed away.

128
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:56,330
I always felt like someone was spying on me.

129
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,320
There is no proof for that

130
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,670
but this vigilance of instinct

131
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,950
has been reminding me

132
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,080
to learn

133
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,310
to hide myself

134
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,000
and to live an average life

135
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:09,090
until such feeling slowly disappeared.

136
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,070
Come to think of it,

137
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:13,350
such stoicism is worthwhile.

138
00:10:15,050 --> 00:10:15,950
Wei Xuan He.

139
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,430
It's time

140
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:21,940
for you to repent.

141
00:10:32,610 --> 00:10:33,660
Xu Xiao Dong,

142
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,480
