149
00:10:56,310 --> 00:10:57,950
Destiny will give you something

150
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,930
that you don't want to face, too.

151
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,740
Soon,

152
00:11:05,730 --> 00:11:06,530
very soon,

153
00:11:06,770 --> 00:11:07,650
very soon,

154
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,870
