165
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,790
Your game fan meeting

166
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:31,920
was a success, right?

167
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,360
You must be very happy

168
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,440
to meet those players who are

169
00:12:35,580 --> 00:12:36,660
in sync with you, right?

170
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:41,820
And this afternoon,

171
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,450
Yuan Yuan told me

172
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:45,910
that we agreed to be

173
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,150
the coolest old ladies

174
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,350
when we grow old.

175
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,790
It's unbelievable.

176
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:52,780
What do you think?

177
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,300
Professor Chen,

178
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,990
isn't there any other way?

179
00:13:53,210 --> 00:13:54,830
I'm willing to do anything if it could

180
00:13:55,060 --> 00:13:56,340
stop Chu Xia from disappearing.

181
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,380
Professor Chen.

182
00:14:00,410 --> 00:14:01,270
Xiao Dong,

183
00:14:02,330 --> 00:14:03,560
Professor Chen has done his best.

184
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,330
There's a way.

