186
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,030
Chu Xia

187
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:11,910
can only exist with the energy

188
00:14:12,030 --> 00:14:13,660
of the gravitational wave

189
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,910
a decade later.

190
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,310
What if she returns to

191
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:19,240
where she lived a decade ago?

192
00:14:19,580 --> 00:14:21,030
She won't need the energy anymore.

193
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,060
She can live like a normal person.

194
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,140
Meaning that

195
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:26,040
if you could fix that machine,

196
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,760
Chu Xia will be fine

197
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:29,510
as she can return to ten years ago.

198
00:14:29,610 --> 00:14:31,640
But the key is I couldn't fix that machine.

199
00:14:32,210 --> 00:14:33,200
I've tried it

200
00:14:33,410 --> 00:14:34,410
