00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:45,659
I promise you

578
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,610
that I'll talk to him.

579
00:34:49,190 --> 00:34:49,840
Thank you.

580
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:50,750
I'm counting on you.

581
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,310
Chu Xia.

582
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,190
As I opposed

583
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,840
the marriage between Xuan He and you,

584
00:35:02,230 --> 00:35:05,800
I always felt guilty about it during this decade

585
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:08,510
when you went missing.

586
00:35:10,640 --> 00:35:11,780
Don't worry about that.

587
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:14,280
I can't believe I'd done

588
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:17,110
many indecorous things that time.

589
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,840
I'd like to apologise.

590
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:27,710
I'm also sorry

591
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:31,590
that things didn't work out

592
00:35:33,570 --> 00:35:35,000
between you and Xuan He.

593
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:36,740
Uncle Wei,

594
00:35:37,150 --> 00:35:38,590
you don't have to worry about it.

595
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,000
I don't think

596
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,570
it's regrettable.

597
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,230
Anyway,

598
00:35:44,670 --> 00:35:45,800
everything happens for a reason.

599
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:49,730
I'll be going now.

600
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,490
I've got some important business
to take care of.

601
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,970
Important business?

602
00:36:02,460 --> 00:36:03,500
[Bing County Part]

603
00:36:35,110 --> 00:36:36,510
I've got to go out later.

604
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:37,570
Complete the tasks

605
00:36:37,650 --> 00:36:39,100
at hand which should be done.

606
00:36:39,670 --> 00:36:40,960
Do not do other things.

607
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,050
Do you hear me?

608
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,310
Do your job.

609
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,500
It's been a long time

610
00:37:18,590 --> 00:37:19,880
since I played Battle of the Saints.

611
00:37:20,070 --> 00:37:20,840
Right.

612
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,780
I can't believe
Battle of the Saints has started charging.

613
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:24,650
Winter said it was permanent free.

614
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,490
Right.

615
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:26,800
The way he plays has also changed.

616
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:28,800
He's started to kill new players.

617
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,070
Don't you think Winter

618
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:31,650
is literally a different person now?

619
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:33,020
He used to care a lot

620
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:34,560
about the fairness and morality
of the gaming world.

621
00:37:34,950 --> 00:37:36,660
He was my idol.

622
00:37:37,030 --> 00:37:38,510
Your idol has ruined his public image.

623
00:37:38,690 --> 00:37:39,960
Our room has collapsed.

624
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,920
I'm sure he is not the Winter I knew.

625
00:37:43,060 --> 00:37:44,310
I'm tired of playing games.

626
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:47,070
Lone Wolves Alliance.

627
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:48,460
Cousin, why are you here?

628
00:37:48,550 --> 00:37:49,450
I need your help.

629
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:50,310
Sure.

630
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:52,480
Lone Wolves Alliance is always available.

631
00:37:53,590 --> 00:37:54,130
Let's go.

632
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:54,970
Sure.

633
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:56,400
Where are you going?

634
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,700
You even try to ditch work.

635
00:38:01,790 --> 00:38:03,140
How dare you?

636
00:38:05,030 --> 00:38:05,960
Brother Sui,

637
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:07,770
I have a favour to ask you.

638
00:38:08,710 --> 00:38:09,630
It's you again.

639
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,670
Just say it.

640
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,140
If you do me

641
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,700
this favour, you'll get my silence

642
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:18,270
about the fact that
Xu Xiao Dong helped you.

643
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,150
If you don't,

644
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:21,140
I'm not too sure

645
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,220
if I'd spill the beans.

646
00:38:24,680 --> 00:38:26,320
Are you eavesdropping?
Three of you, turn around!

647
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:28,280
Young lady,

648
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,230
why are you so immature?

649
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,550
You even threaten me?

650
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:33,510
How would I dare to threaten you?

651
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:38,480
Going to the engineering department
for coordination, right?

652
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:43,790
Right?

653
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,070
Yes.

654
00:38:45,590 --> 00:38:46,550
Make it quick.

655
00:38:46,650 --> 00:38:47,980
We still have a lot of work to do.

656
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:49,280
Let's go.

657
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:58,070
What are you looking at? Do your job.

658
00:39:02,230 --> 00:39:04,570
So this Winter

659
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:06,270
is not the real Winter.

660
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:08,730
That's great.

661
00:39:08,830 --> 00:39:09,780
Winter hasn't changed.

662
00:39:09,860 --> 00:39:11,440
It's only a false alarm.

663
00:39:11,670 --> 00:39:12,480
Does it mean that

664
00:39:12,560 --> 00:39:13,560
I can use my game skin?

665
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,630
And the game is free to play again.

666
00:39:15,710 --> 00:39:16,790
My baby is back too.

667
00:39:16,870 --> 00:39:17,710
It's back.

668
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:19,420
We can play the game again.

669
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:20,140
Hang on.

670
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:21,400
The focus now

671
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,480
is that cousin hopes we could help

672
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:23,580
to maintain the gaming world

673
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:25,320
and wait for the real Winter to come back.

674
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:27,620
No.

675
00:39:28,030 --> 00:39:28,920
Shouldn't the focus

676
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,270
be on the fact that

677
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:32,480
cousin knows Winter

678
00:39:33,080 --> 00:39:34,660
and they're actually good friends?

679
00:39:38,530 --> 00:39:40,280
Maybe we're

680
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:43,390
more than just good friends.

681
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:44,710
What?

682
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,280
He's toast.

683
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:50,210
Xiao Dong's opponent is too strong.

684
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:51,390
Cousin,

685
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,530
come to your senses.

686
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:54,060
Xiao Dong is still there for you.

687
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,270
Cousin,

688
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:56,720
can I meet Winter?

689
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:57,990
Here you go again.

690
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:59,610
What about the steadfast brotherhood

691
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:00,920
between us and Brother Dong?

692
00:40:01,030 --> 00:40:02,670
You only have eyes for idol instead of brothers.

693
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:04,840
Well, I can do that.

694
00:40:05,190 --> 00:40:06,800
Then, count us in.

695
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:09,440
Didn't you talk about

696
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:10,560
the steadfast brotherhood?

697
00:40:13,490 --> 00:40:15,560
Anyway, for Winter,

698
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:16,920
we'll fight!

699
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:19,100
Lone Wolves Alliance.

700
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,400
Easy.

701
00:40:23,590 --> 00:40:24,840
You two hit too hard!

702
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:26,280
-It hurts!
-Easy!

703
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:28,890
Both of you are very annoying!

704
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:32,770
How childish!

705
00:40:36,910 --> 00:40:37,770
Let's go!

706
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:39,630
-We can do it!
-Go, go, go!

707
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,800
-We can do it!
-We can do it!

708
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:42,430
We can do it!

709
00:40:56,020 --> 00:41:01,300
[Turn back]

710
00:41:06,030 --> 00:41:06,850
Dad,

711
00:41:07,070 --> 00:41:08,300
what did you need to see me about?

712
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,800
You still have the audacity to call me?

713
00:41:19,750 --> 00:41:20,570
Let me ask you.

714
00:41:20,690 --> 00:41:22,760
What's wrong with the Family First app?

715
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:26,960
Did you do

716
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:28,760
something shameful?

717
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:33,880
You've disgraced and

718
00:41:33,940 --> 00:41:35,380
humiliated the Wei family!

719
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:38,740
Xuan He,

720
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:41,800
you don't deserve to be my,

721
00:41:42,050 --> 00:41:43,720
Wei Guo Peng's son!

722
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,280
Get lost!

723
00:41:46,700 --> 00:41:47,490
Fine.

724
00:41:51,670 --> 00:41:52,510
I don't want to be

725
00:41:52,610 --> 00:41:54,080
Wei Guo Peng's son, either.

726
00:41:57,550 --> 00:41:58,920
Because you've never

727
00:41:59,670 --> 00:42:00,650
cared about me.

728
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:02,110
I've never had

729
00:42:02,190 --> 00:42:03,820
my father's love since childhood!

730
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:07,940
Do you know how long

731
00:42:08,030 --> 00:42:09,190
it took me to set up Family First?

732
00:42:09,790 --> 00:42:10,650
Do you know how many

733
00:42:10,730 --> 00:42:12,130
days and nights I've spent for this?

734
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:13,710
Do you know how many

735
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:14,940
versions I've created to test run?

736
00:42:15,050 --> 00:42:16,120
You don't know about that.

737
00:42:16,790 --> 00:42:17,790
Because you never

738
00:42:17,870 --> 00:42:19,150
tried to understand me.

739
00:42:21,670 --> 00:42:22,960
Because all you care about are

740
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:25,510
the dignity of this family

741
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:27,210
and your own prestige.

742
00:42:35,670 --> 00:42:36,800
I've already downloaded

743
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:38,850
Family First on your phone.

744
00:42:40,100 --> 00:42:41,590
I guess you've never opened it.
